network-load-balancer
*********************


Description
===========

The properties that define a network load balancer. For more
information, see Introduction to Network Load Balancer.

To use any of the API operations, you must be authorized in an IAM
policy. If you are not authorized, contact an administrator. If you
are an administrator who writes policies to give users access, then
see Getting Started with Policies.

For information about endpoints and signing API requests, see About
the API. For information about available SDKs and tools, see SDKS and
Other Tools.
